<div style="width: 740px; border: 1px dashed gray; padding: 10px;  margin:0px auto;">

<h2>OPD Ophthalmology</h2><hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
This screen will capture Ophthalmology case sheet details.
<br /><hr /><br />
<img src="images/opd_Opthomology.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<hr />
<p>
<span class="title">Decreased Vision: </span><br />
    User can write the Decreased vision Symptoms and Duration of the selected Patient.
<br />
<span class="title">Redness: </span> <br />
User can write the redness Symptoms and duration of the Patient.
<br />
    <span class="title">Pain: </span> 
    <br />User can write the Duration and Symptom of the Pain
<br />
    <span class="title">Discharge: </span> 
    <br />User can write Eye Discharge Details.
<br />
    <span class="title">Floater/Traumaetc: </span> 
    <br />User can write floater and Traumaetc details.
<br />
    <span class="title">Functional Assessment:</span> 
    <br />User can select DM, HTN, Bronchial Asthma, CAD, Autoimmune, Others.
<br />
    <span class="title">Ocular Examinations: </span> 
    <br />User can write Vision details it contains left Eye, Right Eye and PH.
    <br />User can write Distance details it contains left Eye, Right Eye and PH.
    <br />User can write Near details it contains left Eye, Right Eye and PH.
    <br />User can write Refraction details it contains left Eye, Right Eye and PH.
    <br />User can write Acceptance   Distance  details it contains left Eye, Right Eye and PH.
    <br />User can write Acceptance  Near details it contains left Eye, Right Eye and PH.
<br />
    <span class="title">Convergence:</span> 
    <br />User can select from the list, it contains normal and abnormal. If it is abnormal then user can comments.
<br />
    <span class="title">Color Vision:</span> 
    <br />User can select from the list, it contains normal and abnormal. If it is abnormal then user can comments.
<br />
    <span class="title">Ocular Movements: </span> 
    <br />User can select from the list, it contains normal and abnormal. If it is abnormal then user can comments.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Lids: </span> 
    <br />User can select from the list, it contains normal and abnormal. If it is abnormal then user can comments.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Conjunctiva: </span> 
    <br />User can select from the list, it contains normal and abnormal. If it is abnormal then user can comments.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Cornea & AC: </span> 
    <br />User can write Cornea details it contains left Eye, Right Eye.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Ant chamber depth:</span> 
    <br />User can write anti chamber details it contains left Eye, Right Eye.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Cells/flare:</span> 
    <br />User can write cells or flare details it contains left Eye, Right Eye.
    
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">PXF/NVI:</span> 
    <br />User can write pxf or nvi details it contains left Eye, Right Eye.
    
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Pupil Reaction:</span> 
    <br />User can select direct, Consensnal, RAPD
    
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Gonioscopy:</span> 
    <br />User can write gonioscopy details it contains left Eye, Right Eye.
    
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">IOP (months):</span> 
    <br />User can write IOP details it contains left Eye, Right Eye.
    
    <br />
    <hr />
    <br />
    <span class="title">SAC:</span> 
    <br />
    <span class="title">Papillary Dilatation:</span> 
    <br />User can write papillary details it contains left Eye, Right Eye.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Lens:</span> 
    <br />User can write lens details it contains left Eye, Right Eye.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Fundus:</span> 
    <br />User can write fundus details it contains left Eye, Right Eye.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Submit (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on submit button user can save the data. 
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">View (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on view button user can view the previous visit details.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Reset (Button):</span> 
    <br />Clicking on reset button, will clear the current or existing data.
   
</p>
</div>
